---
import TalleyPage from '../../../../../components/talley-wealth/TalleyPage.astro';
import CtaSection from '../../../../../components/talley-wealth/CtaSection.astro';
import { ongoingRhythms, seasonOrder } from '../../../../../data/talley-wealth/ongoing-advisory';

const rhythmLinks = [
  { ...ongoingRhythms[0], href: '/how-we-work/ongoing-advisory/retirement' },
  { ...ongoingRhythms[1], href: '/how-we-work/ongoing-advisory/business-owners' },
  { ...ongoingRhythms[2], href: '/how-we-work/ongoing-advisory/high-earners' },
];
---

<TalleyPage
  title="Ongoing Advisory After Keystone | Talley Wealth"
  description="See how Talley Wealth keeps planning decisions current after Keystone, with annual advisory rhythms for retirement households, business owners, and high earners."
  heroTransparent
>
  <section class="bg-primary pt-32 pb-20 text-primary-foreground sm:pt-40">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">After Keystone</p>
        <h1 class="mt-5 font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-white md:text-6xl">The plan becomes a rhythm.</h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-primary-foreground/82">
          Keystone builds the initial plan. Ongoing advisory is how the right decisions stay visible as tax years close, markets move, business decisions change, and life keeps happening.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-b border-border/50 bg-card">
    <div class="section-container py-8">
      <div class="grid gap-5 text-sm text-muted-foreground md:grid-cols-4">
        <p><strong class="block font-serif text-lg text-primary">Annual Planning Meeting</strong>The core yearly planning session every ongoing advisory client should expect.</p>
        <p><strong class="block font-serif text-lg text-primary">Strategy Session</strong>A second planned touchpoint for year-end, tax, or decision-heavy seasons.</p>
        <p><strong class="block font-serif text-lg text-primary">Work Between Meetings</strong>Analysis, coordination, and implementation keep moving without making every item a meeting.</p>
        <p><strong class="block font-serif text-lg text-primary">Different Emphasis</strong>The structure stays consistent; the decisions change based on what life and money are asking of you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-background py-24">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-primary md:text-4xl">Ongoing advisory is not just "checking in."</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          <p>Most of the useful work happens outside the meeting itself: reviewing tax patterns, watching deadlines, coordinating with other professionals, keeping the portfolio aligned to the plan, and making sure decisions are not waiting until they become urgent.</p>
          <p>The meetings still matter because proactive planning depends on knowing what changed, what matters now, and which decisions deserve attention next.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-14 grid max-w-6xl gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {rhythmLinks.map((rhythm) => (
          <a href={rhythm.href} class="group flex h-full flex-col rounded-lg border border-border/50 bg-card p-7 shadow-elegant transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-elegant-lg">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-accent">{rhythm.eyebrow}</p>
            <h3 class="mt-4 font-serif text-2xl font-bold leading-tight text-primary">{rhythm.shortTitle}</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 flex-1 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">{rhythm.description}</p>
            <span class="mt-6 inline-flex text-sm font-bold text-accent transition group-hover:translate-x-1">See the rhythm <span aria-hidden="true">&nbsp;-&gt;</span></span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-card py-24">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="mx-auto mb-12 max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-primary md:text-4xl">The same four windows show up every year.</h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">The exact work changes by household. The rhythm gives the work a place to live.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-5 md:grid-cols-4">
        {seasonOrder.map((season, index) => (
          <article class="rounded-lg border border-border/50 bg-background p-6 shadow-elegant">
            <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent">{String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</p>
            <h3 class="mt-4 font-serif text-xl font-bold text-primary">{season}</h3>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-background py-24">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">How It Feels</p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-primary md:text-4xl">Prepared, not meeting-heavy.</h2>
          <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">The goal is to do as much as possible without requiring you to meet. But the scheduled meetings still matter because proactive planning depends on knowing you well.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5">
          {[
            'You should not have to remember every planning deadline yourself.',
            'You should not need to translate between the portfolio, the tax return, the estate plan, and the business.',
            'You should know which decisions are already handled, which are waiting, and which ones are not worth your attention right now.',
          ].map((item) => (
            <article class="rounded-lg border border-border/50 bg-card p-6 shadow-elegant">
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">{item}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaSection
    title="Keystone builds the plan. Ongoing advisory keeps it alive."
    description="If you are reviewing Talley Wealth as a possible fit, this is the next chapter the initial planning work is designed to make possible."
    primaryText="Schedule an Explore Call"
  />
</TalleyPage>
